<h2 class="bold font-l">Kermit's rescue attempt</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Kermit attempts to get his fellow muppets onboard to help save Miss Piggy and catch the real thieves, but ends up scaring everyone away, when he mentions the possibility of danger. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
